            <h2>Lesson 1: Introduction to Python</h2>
            <p>Welcome to the first lesson of Python programming. In this lesson, we will cover the basics of Python and how to set up the development environment.</p>
            <h3>What is Python?</h3>
            <p>Python is a high-level, interpreted programming language known for its simplicity and readability. It is widely used for web development, data analysis, machine learning, and more.</p>
            <pre><code>print("Hello, World!")</code></pre>
            <p>In this example, Python prints "Hello, World!" to the console.</p>
            
           
